PN,36301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1772041214
OL,3,CMan who stabbed nine-year-old girl to
OL,4,Cdeath in street jailed
OL,6,FA man who stabbed a nine-year-old girl
OL,7,Fto death as she played in the street
OL,8,Fhas been jailed for at least 25 years.
OL,10,FDeividas Skebas attacked Lilia
OL,11,FValutyte outside the shop where her
OL,12,Fmother was working in Fountain Lane,
OL,13,FBoston, Lincolnshire, in July 2022.
OL,15,FThe Lithuanian national, who had been
OL,16,Fdiagnosed with schizophrenia, admitted
OL,17,Fkilling her but had denied murder,
OL,18,Fclaiming diminished responsibility. He
OL,19,Fwas found guilty after a trial earlier
OL,20,Fthis month.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
