OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1772041214
OL,3,CMan who stabbed nine-year-old girl to
OL,4,Cdeath in street jailed
OL,6,FThe 26-year-old appeared at Lincoln
OL,7,FCrown Court for sentencing via a video
OL,8,Flink from Rampton high security
OL,9,Fhospital.
OL,11,FDuring the trial, jurors were told
OL,12,Fthat Skebas had a history of mental
OL,13,Fhealth issues and had been detained in
OL,14,Fhospital under the Mental Health Act
OL,15,Fin 2020.
OL,17,FHe was discharged from the hospital
OL,18,Fand returned to Lithuania but legally
OL,19,Fre-entered the UK on 2 July 2022 -
OL,20,Fless than four weeks before he
OL,21,Fmurdered Lilia on 28 July.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1772041214
OL,3,CMan who stabbed nine-year-old girl to
OL,4,Cdeath in street jailed
OL,6,FHe was initially found unfit to stand
OL,7,Ftrial and a trial of facts was held a
OL,8,Fyear later, when a jury found Skebas
OL,9,Fhad carried out the killing.
OL,11,FHe only faced trial for murder
OL,12,Ffollowing an improvement in his mental
OL,13,Fhealth.
OL,15,FA report by three psychiatrists said
OL,16,FSkebas had schizophrenia and was
OL,17,Fshowing symptoms of psychosis on the
OL,18,Fday he killed Lilia.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1772041214
OL,3,CMan who stabbed nine-year-old girl to
OL,4,Cdeath in street jailed
OL,6,FCCTV footage from the scene showed him
OL,7,Fwatching Lilia play with a hula hoop
OL,8,Fin the moments before he walked up and
OL,9,Fstabbed her. He then ran from the
OL,10,Fscene.
OL,12,FThe court heard he had bought the
OL,13,Fmurder weapon - a paring knife - two
OL,14,Fdays earlier from a nearby Wilko shop.
OL,16,FAfter the killing he contacted family
OL,17,Fin Lithuania asking for money in order
OL,18,Fto leave the country. He also shaved
OL,19,Foff his beard.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1772041214
OL,3,CMan who stabbed nine-year-old girl to
OL,4,Cdeath in street jailed
OL,6,FThe jury rejected Skebas's claims of
OL,7,Fdiminished responsibility after the
OL,8,Fprosecution argued the killing was a
OL,9,F"wicked act" and was "deliberate and
OL,10,Fplanned".
OL,12,FDuring the sentencing hearing
OL,13,Fprosecutor Christopher Donnellan KC
OL,14,Fsaid Lilia was a "particularly
OL,15,Fvulnerable victim".
OL,17,FAndrew Campbell-Tiech, mitigating,
OL,18,Ftold the court Skebas had a "serious
OL,19,Fand dangerous condition for many
OL,20,Fyears".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1772041214
OL,3,CMan who stabbed nine-year-old girl to
OL,4,Cdeath in street jailed
OL,6,FHe said there was "no need further to
OL,7,Fstigmatise the appalling act that he
OL,8,Fperformed in the midst of a mental
OL,9,Fhealth crisis".
OL,11,FThe judge said the court had to decide
OL,12,Fif Skebas's mental state "lessened his
OL,13,Fculpability to an extent".
OL,15,FLilia's parents were in court for the
OL,16,Fsentencing, listening to proceedings
OL,17,Ftranslated into Lithuanian through
OL,18,Fheadphones.
OL,20,FMore to follow.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
